To check whether the given numbers are odd or even
Create a slider n from 1 to 1000000000000000000000000
Create a input box linking n
Hide the slider
Create a text box "To check whether the given number is even or odd"
If(n>=0,"Check whether the given number is even or odd","Remove the minus sign before the number then go to step-2")
If(n<0,"Remove the minus sign before the number",If(Mod(n,2)==0,"The number is even","The number is odd"))
Create a check box to show step-2
End.

https://www.geogebra.org/m/rgycka2v
